### Overall quality
The codebase has strong test discipline. `tls.rs`, `agent_liveness.rs`, and `agents.rs` are exemplary. The main gap is in `api.rs` — three REST endpoints (`GET /listeners/{name}`, `GET /webhooks`, and the `create_listener` error paths) have no direct test coverage despite being part of the documented public API surface.
